description: Denominator of [x^(2n+1)] in the Taylor expansion arcsinh(cosec(x)-cot(x))= x/2 +x^3/48 +x^5/768 +61*x^7/645120 +277*x^9/37158912 +..
comments: Numerators are apparently covered by A091912.The e.g.f. of x/2, arcsinh(cosec(x)-cot(x)) = x/(2^1*1!) + x^3/(2^3*3!) +5*x^5/(2^5*5!) +61*x^7/(2^7*7!) +1385*x^9/(2^9*9!) +... is apparently provided by the absolute values of A028296.
author: Patrick Demichel (patrick.demichel(AT)hp.com)
extensions: Values replaced by denominators. - R. J. Mathar, Dec 19 2011
